    "In our results, we refer to these optimization strategies as baseline and distillation.",
    "In all cases, we rescaled spatial and temporal coordinates to [-1, 1].",
    "Image reconstruction quality was assessed using SSIM and PSNR metrics to evaluate global intensity and structural reconstruction, respectively.",
    "Segmentation quality was measured using the Dice similarity coefficient (DSC).",
    "All metrics were averages over 100 patients."
